faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, skopje<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科索沃：prizren<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, prishtina<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希臘：thessaloniki，athens<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：代表值得去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔值得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：可去可唔去"},{"pid":"5e459464771dde742fd89ba5a568a161601d763b","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚想去巴爾幹但唔敢，lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打完仗好耐啦<br />\n你估仲係歐洲軍火庫咩</blockquote><br />\n我唔係驚戰火，我知依家果邊好和平，不過一個人都係驚架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係d夜晚唔行小路嘅廢話tips，不過有一晚係kotor真係幾驚，前一晚係duborvnik有個架妹話差d比人強姦，咁我都驚俾人搶野。果日1點先落車，攞住自拍棍行返hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2245899974481bf656f2866be38fb77718092c5a","tid":125201,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"波斯尼亞緊係去薩拉熱窩同Mostar<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce832821e4a14be323afbc100896f9668184f30","tid":125201,"uid":5435,"like":0,"d