\" />,sighisoara<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, sighet marmatiei<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (加烏克蘭買vodka），suceava <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑山：budva<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> + sveti stefan, kotor +perast<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n克羅地亞：dubrovnik<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n波斯尼亞：trebinje小鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿爾巴尼亞：tirana<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,berat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬其頓：ohrid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, skopje<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科索沃：prizren<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, prishtina<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希臘：thessaloniki，athens<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：代表值得去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔值得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：可去可唔去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身想去果邊 但果邊內陸  鐘意海邊多啲<br />\n所以揀左沿海<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/185807_f62358053c434f5d59401ac9c84a9926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F185807_f62358053c434f5d59401ac9c84a9926.jpg&h=620c1ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPlan 緊兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等巴打去埋希臘果邊賽後報告"},{"pid":"ce77f769cc343dae6297016a7f8c9f1fa9df8ee1","tid":125201,"uid":5435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>7月會去zadar split Dubrovnik budva kotor <br />\n巴打有咩意見</blockquote><br />\nbudva：其實無咩野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你當迷你版dubrovnik就得，有沙灘啱鬼佬鬼妹渡假，hk人未必啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nkotor：我淨係玩左1日，如果你想hea d可以2日，一定要上山頂睇kotor峽灣好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上到中段見到交通可以停，又或者繼續挑戰自己上埋去（雖然再上d景無咩特別）<br />\ndubrovnik：其實都係上城牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚貴成人150kn（好彩學生50je），見到有間係懸崖嘅bar可以去下應該幾正，古城好乾淨好新（應該翻新完），不過物價係同西歐有得比<br />\nzadar split無去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問學生證個問題，係咪要整張咩國際學生證？<br />\n定用自己大學果張都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aee9d2646a9b9b67f42a9288d625b0e4b2c63fc","tid":125201,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>7月會去zadar split Dubrovnik