e72671b93c92d4b0c88cf6","tid":125201,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"講多啲 Albania <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f064d04cc7e4b008cf04cb3674e272281cbcb3","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多啲 Albania <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n景點： 話說阿爾巴尼亞俾人形容到好差好落後咁，但係佢近幾年develop得算幾快。我去過陣首都ge 斯坎培德廣場就大維修緊，無開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tirana嘅景點相對集中， 10分鐘基本上行得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有個遠d嘅景點叫bunkart，係一個防核戰嘅地堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當地人都幾推薦，不過我覺得有 creepy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nberat呢個小鎮最有特色就係佢d好多窗嘅屋，舊城城堡都值得上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貨幣： 1euro 大約133lek，一舊byrek 30lek超抵<br />\n飲食：byrek是常識吧，仲有係舊城有間最古老嘅酒店（其實都係2x年），食過嘅芝士釀豬排都幾好食，係咪當地先有就唔清楚<br />\n交通：最on9就係交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無時間表可言，問下當地人算啦，好似我第二日由berat到馬其頓嘅ohrid，hostel，網上都話搭去elbassan轉巴士到struga或者qafe thane or pogradec<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朝早11點到elbassan都話成日都無車去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d路好似車震咁，90km行3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b213e2c1a7dd9630198b7f5de8a02d46c7227a5","tid":125201,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb 跟住Budapest走.....咁樣玩順路嗎?  <br />\n定係維也納落去方便d?"},{"pid":"1ebacce23c611b1e278033f81d8a62503aaf7f0f","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb 跟住Budapest走.....咁樣玩順路嗎?  <br />\n定係維也納落去方便d?</blockquote><br />\n克羅地亞無你想像中咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />budapest落zagreb，十六湖，zadar，split,dubrovnik係順路，但係你諗住點樣由dubrovnik走翻上vienna/budapest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeacc7adfe9d1e5ca733847758b112823c4491bf","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb 跟住Budapest走.....咁樣玩順路嗎?  <br />\n定係維也納落去方便d?</blockquote><br />\n克羅地亞無你想像中咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />budapest落zagreb，十六湖，zadar，split,dubrovnik係順路，但係你諗住點樣由dubrovnik走翻上vienna/budapest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndubrovnik去zagreb好似10個鐘巴士唔係好記得"},{"pid":"4a741f29f4c17972b33991c7f4458fcc010993e7","tid":125201,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb 跟住Budapest走.....咁樣玩順路嗎?  <br />\n定係維也納落去方便d?</blockquote><br />\n克羅地亞無你想像中咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />budapest落zagreb，十六湖，zadar，split,dubrovnik係順路，但係你諗住點樣由dubrovnik走翻上vienna/budapest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndubrovnik去zagreb好似10個鐘巴士唔係好記得</blockquote><br />\n到時可能搭夜巴/內陸機返Zagreb掛~~而家諗緊Budapest 來回方唔方便....因為Vienna 機票都貴Budapest成千蚊....唔知Budapest有無野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 另外女友去過奧地利所以無所謂, 但今次一定要落Dubrovnik 玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 識揸車, 諗緊去到克羅地亞再一路揸落去, 跟住內陸機返Zagreb"},{"pid":"1819c7fed06adbee562a20fbdbfa1392d3cb7141","tid":125201,"uid":39494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb 跟住Budapest走.....咁樣玩順路嗎?  <br />\n定係維也納落去方便d?</blockquote><br />\n其實dubrovnik返zagreb搭內陸機早買都係幾舊水, 唔係真係貴長途巴士好多<br />\n來往匈牙利同克羅地亞剩係得陸路, 如果你諗住剩係為左搭飛機走由dubronik返budapest嘅話其實好浪費時間<br />\n不如open jaw由zagreb走或者由玩埋第二度後飛返budapest, 附近嘅話sarajevo同podgorica都有直航去budapest"},{"pid":"53cc22e2c777184a87a7878a55b89e620fee5724","tid":125201,"uid":39494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb 跟住Budapest走.....咁樣玩順路嗎?  <br />\n定係維也納落去方便d?</blockquote><br />\n克羅地亞無你想像中咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />budapest落zagreb，十六湖，zadar，split,dubrovnik係順路，但係你諗住點樣由dubrovnik走翻上vienna/budapest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndubrovnik去zagreb好似10個鐘巴士唔係好記得</blockquote><br />\n到時可能搭夜巴/內陸機返Zagreb掛~~而家諗緊Budapest 來回方唔方便....因為Vienna 機票都貴Budapest成千蚊....唔知Budapest有無野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 另外女友去過奧地利所以無所謂, 但今次一定要落Dubrovnik 玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 識揸車, 諗緊去到克羅地亞再一路揸落去, 跟住內陸機返Zagreb</blockquote><br />\nbudapest真心推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而聽過wien悶到抽筋, 物價又貴<br />\n想玩埋wien其實可以由budapest搭火車上, 都係兩個幾鐘路程"},{"pid":"b2c2cf8d81afe2b293e4d4d029fcf81af9931865","tid":125201,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f58c80589193997e4289b5729adf7a483f987a0","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下我同女友諗住8月飛, 由Budapest 落去克羅地亞再玩到Dubrovnik....之後再返轉頭去返zagreb