es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n時間上我覺得ok，如果接受到夜車我計過可以去買sarajevo同mostar 添。有d地方去得幾急，e.g. duborvnik得半日但係夠我係新城同舊城都鳩行3個鐘，行埋城牆，再跟個2個鐘ge free walking tour（果日7點出發）<br />\n最hea嘅地方係ohrid，真係太靚我stay咗兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過體力真係幾chur，你預隨時每日都行30000步/15k，尤其爬kotor berat個d城墻唔算輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f5c9f49a2e37ea06c4b99054479d20b81e4ad3","tid":125201,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34223e88115a7ef26dfad025e3f06aed716ebd44","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n17 日會唔會唔夠? 如果再去你會預幾多日?</blockquote><br />\n一定唔夠，今次絕對係走馬看花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果想走晒成個巴爾幹（即係仲有保加利亞，塞爾維亞），我諗至少35日</blockquote><br />\n係咪好趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n時間上我覺得ok，如果接受到夜車我計過可以去買sarajevo同mostar 添。有d地方去得幾急，e.g. duborvnik得半日但係夠我係新城同舊城都鳩行3個鐘，行埋城牆，再跟個2個鐘ge free walking tour（果日7點出發）<br />\n最hea嘅地方係ohrid，真係太靚我stay咗兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過體力真係幾chur，你預隨時每日都行30000步/15k，尤其爬kotor berat個d城墻唔算輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冶安點? 買野找錢會唔會找少左或者冇啦啦叫你比tips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你當聽唔明佢哋up乜就得，我係budva食過一餐海鮮餐成30eur，埋單嗰陣聽到waitor講乜嘢service service,走左先至係tips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比錢round up好正常，尤其羅馬尼亞進做十位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試過比佢無找錢，佢當咗tips，不過小過1euro就算"},{"pid":"421fdb8d3887574d83a23e63ed2f9c7553467cf9","tid":125201,"uid":45553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:26:15.000Z","msg":"搭過最長時間嘅巴士係幾耐"},{"pid":"1d1cd271f0a53a694c28ae71ec692409ec5f8da7","tid":125201,"uid":9496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多啲 Albania <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n景點： 話說阿爾巴尼亞俾人形容到好差好落後咁，但係佢近幾年develop得算幾快。我去過陣首都ge 斯坎培德廣場就大維修緊，無開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tirana嘅景點相對集中， 10分鐘基本上行得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有個遠d嘅景點叫bunkart，係一個防核戰嘅地堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當地人都幾推薦，不過我覺得有 creepy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nberat呢個小鎮最有特色就係佢d好多窗嘅屋，舊城城堡都值得上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貨幣： 1euro 大約133lek，一舊byrek 30lek超抵<br />\n飲食：byrek是常識吧，仲有係舊城有間最古老嘅酒店（其實都係2x年），食過嘅芝士釀豬排都幾好食，係咪當地先有就唔清楚<br />\n交通：最on9就係交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無時間表可言，問下當地人算啦，好似我第二日由berat到馬其頓嘅ohrid，hostel，網上都話搭去elbassan轉巴士到struga或者qafe thane or pogradec<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朝早11點到elbassan都話成日都無車去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d路好似車震咁，90km行3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係Albania有冇比啲local用奇怪眼神望住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次同個friend去Albania 啲人好似未見過黃種人咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有啲人走黎問可唔可以同你影張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2003cdf3e3d8b8040d0837921fd312f5ea3204d1","tid":125201,"uid":56765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"之前去左十日克羅地亞 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想再去！"},{"pid":"6c734552858d8913471a4757e529683a1c60b09f","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭過最長時間嘅巴士係幾耐</blockquote><br />\n6個幾鐘，由kotor去tirana，其實車好就唔辛苦，albania 3個鐘車真係死得人"},{"pid":"bcdd63304d000e8491b0a379b7804aa32feffb86","tid":125201,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講多啲 Albania <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n景點： 話說阿爾巴尼亞俾人形容到好差好落後咁，但係佢近幾年develop得算幾快。我去過陣首都ge 斯坎培德廣場就大維修緊，無開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tirana嘅景點相對集中， 10分鐘基本上行得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有個遠d嘅景點叫bunkart，係一個防核戰嘅地堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當地人都幾推薦，不過我覺得有 creepy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nberat呢個小鎮最有特色就係佢d好多窗嘅屋，舊城城堡都值得上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貨幣： 1euro 大約133lek，一舊byrek 30lek超抵<br />\n飲食：byrek是常識吧，仲有係舊城有間最古老嘅酒店（其實都係2x年），食過嘅芝士釀豬排都幾好食，係咪當地先有就唔清楚<br />\n交通：最on9就係交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無時間表可言，問下當地人算啦，好似我第二日由berat到馬其頓嘅ohrid，hostel，網上都話搭去elbassan轉巴士到struga或者qafe thane or pogradec<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朝早11點到elbassan都話成日都無車去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d路好似車震咁，90km行3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係Albania有冇比啲local用奇怪眼神望住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次同個friend去Albania 啲人好似未見過黃種人咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有啲人走黎問可唔可以同你影張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl